It is possible to define up to 5 "hard" attributes linked to the customer master data.
These attributes can be viewed, populated, and filtered just like any other field within the customer card.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001034-0/SetAttributi_ENU.jpg"><br>

After defining the "hard" attributes, once Business Central is reopened, the defined fields will be directly visible in the customer master data card.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001034-0/SetAttributi2_ENU.jpg"><br>